article.headline: Spinoso scores 23 to help Pennsylvania knock off Columbia 84-72

images.name: Penn Claims Ivy Win Over Columbia  - Via Ivy League
images.caption: Penn's Clark Slajchert and Nick Spinoso Combine For 45 Points in Win Over Columbia

article.linkText: Spinoso scores 23 to help Pennsylvania knock off Columbia 84-72
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Nick Spinoso had 23 points in Pennsylvania's 84-72 victory against Columbia on Saturday night. Spinoso added nine rebounds and five assists for the Quakers (11-17, 3-10 Ivy League). Clark Slajchert shot 8 for 11, including 4 for 5 from beyond the arc, scoring 22. Tyler Perkins sank three 3-pointers and scored 13. Geronimo Rubio De La Rosa led the Lions (13-13, 4-9) with 15 points. Zavian McLean had 14 points and six rebounds, while Blair Thompson scored 13. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
